text:
Nice ktv area with rotation to every table.

Nice vocal singing at the bar that night while I was there.

Friendly staff who are welcoming and nice. Tried asking freebies and yes they gave us hello pandas and fish ball crackers.

Not much food item in the menu, mostly air fried kind of food. ($16 for this tiny bowl of Sotong ball)
It’s a good and relaxing bar, when you keen to just have a drink and chill,
Nice bar to have a good drink with friends! Price is reasonable and ambience is great!
Homely place with friendly staff and good karaoke system! Doesn’t matter if you come alone or with a group of friends, you will have a good time!
Very nice place! Recommended bar in sg. Come here and feel it!
